  <summary date="2022-04-22T15:11:27Z" status="Introduced in House">Fresh Start Act of 2021

This bill authorizes the Department of Justice to award grants for states to implement automatic expungement laws (i.e., laws that provide for the automatic expungement or sealing of an individual's criminal records).</summary>
